Thirty-two male Sprague Dawley rats were treated with LPS (0.5 mg/kg) or saline vehicle (1 ml/kg) and scanned 24 hours later. T2-weighted images and multi-shell diffusion MRI data were acquired on a 9.4T Bruker BioSpec 94/20.

This dataset has been converted using BrkRaw (https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3818615) at 2022-10-07 18:12:45.343116.
